{\*\generator Msftedit 5.41.15.1515;}\viewkind4\uc1\pard\cf1\b\f0\fs20 This example shows to use Headers and Footers.\par
\par
\i\f1 Page Headers \i0\f0 and\i\f1  \cf2 Page Footers\cf1  \i0\f0 are set up in \cf2 I/O Properties\cf1 , and print automatically at the top of each page.\par
\par
\i\f1 Control break\i0\f0  Headers and Footers are printed manually, using \cf2 Group \cf1 logic units. These repeat automatically when there is a page break.\par
\par
To use this example, just press Start and the report will be printed. Comments inside the program explain the details. You can also use the Debugger to step through the logic while it executes.\par
